      },
      "date": "2024-03-08 02:17:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Interesting that this patch is left homeless:\n > ldiskfs/kernel_patches/patches/base/ext4-reset-exts-for-gcc10.patch\n > \n > Also the kernel patches as well as:\n > config/lustre-build-ldiskfs.m4:36:\t83)     LDISKFS_SERIES=\"4.18-rhel8.3.series\"\n >    ;;\n > ought to be dropped.\n\nI will pick that up in a separate patch to remove the el8.[0-3] kernel patch series.",
